    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Up for sale is a mechanically robust E92 M3, powered by the high-revving 4.0L S65 V8 engine. This naturally aspirated unit features eight individual throttle bodies and a specialized ionic current knock sensing system, delivering 414 horsepower with a visceral 8,400 RPM redline. The powertrain is mated to a precise 6-speed manual transmission and a GKN-sourced M Variable Differential Lock, ensuring optimal power delivery through the rear wheels. The suspension architecture retains its factory-spec rigidity, featuring aluminum control arms and Electronic Damping Control (EDC) for selectable valve adjustment. Recent preventative maintenance includes an analysis of the rod bearings and replacement of the throttle actuators, ensuring the valvetrain and induction systems operate at peak efficiency. This chassis offers a pure, analog driving experience with the technical sophistication expected of BMW\u2019s final naturally aspirated M flagship.",
      "price": 34500.0,
